                     <note>F1a: impression of rectangular Persian seal of Archibald Swinton Rustam Jang Bahadur, dated 1174 (1760-1) and regnal year 2. Inside front cover: armorial bookplate of Gordon of Buthlaw. Some headings in red.</note>
